    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5382273/" class="title-link">文化多元主义的谬误和进步文明的困境</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5382273"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/37082124/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u37082124-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/37082124/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">sonkey</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-10"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-10 01:04:55</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5382273_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一．  种族歧视一定是不正确的吗         种族问题在中国一直不算什么大问题，而在西方国家却如同在我国“拥护国家拥护党”一样的作为政治正确。马丁路德金领导的黑人民权运动一直被弘扬为可歌可泣的典范。美国人在日常事务上，最怕被贴上“种族歧视”的标签，此类问题如果惹上...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5382273/#comments">(8回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">90有用 / 5没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            Regnery Publishing, Inc.2006版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5382273_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5382273_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7331360">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7331360/" class="title-link">孤单的美国：欧洲的穆斯林化和西方的衰落</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7331360"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

